Compiled feedback exports land here. The content agent reads `latest.md`.

Workflow:
1. In the app, open the floating 💬 → Log tab → Copy compiled markdown
2. Paste contents into `data/feedback/latest.md`
3. Commit + push
4. Trigger the content agent (Actions → Content agent → Run workflow)
5. Review the resulting draft PR

See scripts/agent/README.md for full setup.
